    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 represents a superlative example of the E46 chassis, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This collector-grade specimen has been meticulously maintained, with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The 6-speed manual transmission delivers power to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction and cornering dynamics. Finished in showroom-quality paint with a pristine interior, the vehicle retains its factory-spec suspension geometry and bushings, offering the precise, analog feedback enthusiasts crave. A turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
