      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-standard vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing, and the original 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a documented single-owner pedigree, this is an investment-grade specimen suitable for the most demanding collector. Included are all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
